{"tid":1355334,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民主派要求召開特別會議","createTime":"2019-07-23T09:40:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T12:56:06.000Z","uid":212626,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c54d322a5864dfe0a009b63591436d55cfc38dad","tid":1355334,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T09:40:54.000Z","msg":"民主派24位立法會議員向立法會主席梁君彥發公開信，要求盡快召開特別會議討論元朗事件。<br />\n<br />\n民主派指出，周日元朗發生涉嫌警黑勾結事件，警方被社會廣泛視為縱容黑社會持械毆打平民百姓達數小時，翌日僅6人就有關事件被捕。<br />\n<br />\n他們認為，林鄭政府有必要清楚交代元朗事件，強烈要求根據《議事規則》盡快召開特別會議討論元朗事件，並要求特首林鄭月娥、保安局局長李家超、警務處處長盧偉聰及其他相關官員列席，就警方當日的作為及不作為交代及道歉。<br />\n<br />\n另外，民主派議員將會尋求在最短時間內提出議案譴責何君堯。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2198405/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2198405%2F&d=DQhhZyJ%2BQntsVA7gHYVTWDMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=f0abf65e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2198405/</a>"},{"pid":"22a1d3142160cf0efe7c9bd78fbe1b5f1b37c89b","tid":1355334,"uid":212626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T09:42:17.000Z","msg":"議事規則<br />\n15. 處理急切事項的會議 <br />\n<br />\n(1) 立法會主席須應行政長官的要求召開立法會緊急會議。如須在立法會任期完結或解散之後的期間舉行緊急會議，會議應在指明舉行選出立法會議員的換屆選舉的日期(如多於一日，則為首日)前召開。 (2017年第186號法律公告) <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">(2) 在立法會一個會期結束而下一會期仍未開始的一段休假期內，立法會主席可在其指定的日期及時間召開特別會議。 </span><br />\n<br />\n(3) 本議事規則適用於根據第(1)及(2)款舉行的立法會會議。 (2017年第186號法律公告)"},{"pid":"28c950f72a466e21adccdeead7814e1e4a8265de","tid":1355334,"uid":212626,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T09:43:29.000Z","msg":"將個波拋咗俾大口彥<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7e0dcc0388ad31ebce1aa20cb7e64913c4fb558","tid":1355334,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T09:44:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8853e67a66ea0cbb83c41610e9ab7892d0edb16","tid":1355334,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T09:47:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92ac1184a69ec33452f6c6c4dcae802bb96129a2","tid":1355334,"uid":269711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T09:48:13.000Z","msg":"１。全面撤回送中<br />\n２。撤銷暴動定性<br />\n３。釋放被捕義士並承諾永不追究<br />\n４。全面實行雙普選<br />\n５。成立獨立調查委員會追究黑警責任＋徹查警黑勾結元朗暴動"},{"pid":"2a40336eb0e697d4b166c31c6533edd4f937bb78","tid":1355334,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T10:10:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"106ff125b594e23894f2b2f3b658ef7882facee1","tid":1355334,"uid":212738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T10:11:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d271a1f04951e6bb0afc3a58f6d83e73b92d5602","tid":1355334,"uid":64159,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"28c950f72a466e21adccdeead7814e1e4a8265de","tid":1355334,"uid":212626,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T09:43:29.000Z","msg":"將個波拋咗俾大口彥<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T10:12:37.000Z","msg":"唔駛睇都知唔會開，<br />\n你見班建制唔出聲講元朗就知咩事"},{"pid":"bf0df89fc6f983c49c7374dcc5d7a0d85e01f23b","tid":1355334,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T10:34:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71184575781cfb379fa436d2f277f1e3d6c71f3f","tid":1355334,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:49:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55f3a3b8b64a5daab3375615d72df250925d285d","tid":1355334,"uid":268623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:51:11.000Z","msg":"洗乜開會幫政府拆彈呀，而家講緊呢個立法會無合法性，要真雙普選，你果頭走去開會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d229eb2bf7e9904a66545cf85cd8ce3fabd85dd","tid":1355334,"uid":149361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:56:06.000Z","msg":"我覺得唔好搞何妖個位 何妖一日仲係建制議員 對抗爭活動有利<br />\n<br />\n踢佢走等於佢可以同建制陣營某程度上割蓆"}]}